K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156a-1: a'arya n'a ga r'a dza pa ri pri tstsha n'a ma dh'a ra n'i /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156a-3: 'phags pa klu'i rgyal po gzi can gyis zhus pa zhes bya ba'i gzungs /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156a-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156a-6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156a-7: bcom ldan 'das yul ma ga dha na lus 'phags ri'i dbang po brag phug na bzhugs te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156a-8: de nas klu'i rgyal po gzi can kha dog shin tu 'phags pa dang ldan pa nam sros pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156a-9: bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der song ste phyin nas bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la mgo pos phyag 'tshal te //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156a-10: bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156a-12: lus 'phags ri 'di na ring po dag dge slong rnams la 'tshe na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156a-13: de la bdag gis ji ltar mi 'tshe bar bgyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156a-14: de skad ces gsol pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156b-0: @156b bcom ldan 'das kyis klu'i rgyal po gzi can la 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156b-1: klu'i rgyal po legs so legs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156b-2: 'di lta bu ni khyod kyi bya ba yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156b-3: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong rnams la bka' stsal pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156b-6: sman chen po bco brgyad po 'di dag gi ming zungs shig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156b-22: ae kar sh'i ta ram g'a prishti /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156b-25: sman chen po bco brgyad po de dag gi ming 'dzin pa de'i lus la rims kyis mi tshugs /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156b-34: de la ring po dag 'tshe bar mi 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156b-35: su zhig 'di dag 'dzin pa de ji srid 'tsho'i bar du srung ba byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156b-36: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:156b-37: klu'i rgyal po gzi can yid rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-017:157a-1: can gyi zhus pa zhes bya ba'i gzungs rdzogs so ////
